{"title":"Coefficient Wave RR handlebar gives you an ultra-aero position, no illegal tuck needed","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/03/01/coefficient-wave-rr-handlebar-give-you-an-ultra-aero-position-no-illegal-tuck-needed/","date":1614632730000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><p>The new Coefficient Wave RR handlebar takes its shaping to extremes to produce a more comfortable bar that puts you in a more ergonomic, aerodynamic position.</p><p>Called Swope, the Wave RR (for “Road Race”) handlebar uses a riser shape that then slopes downward to the hoods. That, plus thumb grooves and palm recesses throughout provide a plethora of hand positions that are among the most comfortable I’ve ever found on a handlebar. First up, tech specs and details, then my first impressions…</p><h2>Coefficient RR tech details</h2><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Coefficient-Wave-RR-handlebar-top.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Coefficient-Wave-RR-handlebar-top.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs:484x240/rscb8/ng:webp/ngcb8\" alt=\"coefficient wave rr aero ergonomic road bike handlebar\" width=\"1400\" height=\"695\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1400px) 100vw, 1400px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Coefficient-Wave-RR-handlebar-top.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs:484x240/rscb8/ng:webp/ngcb8\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Coefficient-Wave-RR-handlebar-top.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 1400w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Coefficient-Wave-RR-handlebar-top-297x147.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Coefficient-Wave-RR-handlebar-top-800x397.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Coefficient-Wave-RR-handlebar-top-120x60.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Coefficient-Wave-RR-handlebar-top-768x381.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Coefficient-Wave-RR-handlebar-top-696x346.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Coefficient-Wave-RR-handlebar-top-1068x530.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Coefficient-Wave-RR-handlebar-top-846x420.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 846w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Coefficient-Wave-RR-handlebar-top-324x160.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 324w\" ezoid=\"0.7365996683589391\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Coefficient-Wave-RR-handlebar-top.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 1400w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Coefficient-Wave-RR-handlebar-top-297x147.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Coefficient-Wave-RR-handlebar-top-800x397.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Coefficient-Wave-RR-handlebar-top-120x60.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Coefficient-Wave-RR-handlebar-top-768x381.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Coefficient-Wave-RR-handlebar-top-696x346.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Coefficient-Wave-RR-handlebar-top-1068x530.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Coefficient-Wave-RR-handlebar-top-846x420.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 846w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Coefficient-Wave-RR-handlebar-top-324x160.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 324w\"></a></p><p>The RR uses a unique shape all over, but most noticeable from the top is the integrated computer mount bridge. This isn’t just a very fancy, overwrought way to hold your GPS cycling computer, though. It’s there to provide a platform for your thumbs to wrap around while your palm rests on the rise to either side of the stem’s mounting point.</p><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Coefficient-Wave-RR-handlebar-front.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Coefficient-Wave-RR-handlebar-front.jpg\" alt=\"coefficient wave rr aero ergonomic road bike handlebar\" width=\"1400\" height=\"524\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1400px) 100vw, 1400px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Coefficient-Wave-RR-handlebar-front.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Coefficient-Wave-RR-handlebar-front.jpg 1400w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Coefficient-Wave-RR-handlebar-front-297x111.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Coefficient-Wave-RR-handlebar-front-800x299.jp