lly correct angle that has the dual benefit of positioning your arms in a narrow, more aerodynamic position.</p><p>They say it also puts your shoulders in an optimal position and improves core stability and breathing mechanics. All this because you’re hands and arms are more relaxed by being better aligned.</p><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/coefficient-RR-ergo-aero-road-bike-handlebar-shapes-01.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/coefficient-RR-ergo-aero-road-bike-handlebar-shapes-01.jpg\" alt=\"coefficient wave rr aero ergonomic road bike handlebar\" width=\"1200\" height=\"901\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/coefficient-RR-ergo-aero-road-bike-handlebar-shapes-01.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/coefficient-RR-ergo-aero-road-bike-handlebar-shapes-01.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/coefficient-RR-ergo-aero-road-bike-handlebar-shapes-01-297x223.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/coefficient-RR-ergo-aero-road-bike-handlebar-shapes-01-800x601.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/coefficient-RR-ergo-aero-road-bike-handlebar-shapes-01-120x90.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/coefficient-RR-ergo-aero-road-bike-handlebar-shapes-01-768x577.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/coefficient-RR-ergo-aero-road-bike-handlebar-shapes-01-696x523.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.c