ikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/coefficient-RR-ergo-aero-road-bike-handlebar-shapes-02-560x420.jpg 560w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/coefficient-RR-ergo-aero-road-bike-handlebar-shapes-02-80x60.jpg 80w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/coefficient-RR-ergo-aero-road-bike-handlebar-shapes-02-265x198.jpg 265w\"></a></p><p>The drops use a compound curve design that’s fairly common, but add an indent for your thumb that provides a surprisingly useful little perch.</p><p>Basic specs and measurements are the same across all widths (38/40/42/44), with a few size-specific ones. Here’s what’s shared:</p><ul><li>Clamp diameter: 31.8mm</li><li>Drop: 127mm</li><li>Reach: 77mm</li><li>Slope: 12º</li><li>Sweep: 16º</li><li>Flare: 7º</li><li>Stem-to-Computer (center to center): 87mm</li><li>Clamp area width: 56mm</li></ul><figure id=\"attachment_252273\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-252273\"><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/coefficient-RR-ergo-aero-road-bike-handlebar-actual-weights-01.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/coefficient-RR-ergo-aero-road-bike-handlebar-actual-weights-01.jpg\" alt=\"coefficient wave rr handlebar actual weight for size 42 cm width\" width=\"1200\" height=\"352\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/coefficient-RR-ergo-aero-road-bike-handlebar-actual-weights-01.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/coefficient-RR-ergo-aero-road-bike-handlebar-actual-weights-01.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/coefficient-RR-ergo-aero-road-bike-handlebar-actual-weights-01-297x87.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/coefficient-RR-ergo-aero-road-bike-handlebar-actual-weights-01-800x235.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/coefficient-RR-ergo-aero-road-bike-handlebar-actual-weights-01-120x35.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/coefficient-RR-ergo-aero-road-bike-handlebar-actual-weights-01-768x225.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/coefficient-RR-ergo-aero-road-bike-handlebar-actual-weights-01-696x204.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/coefficient-RR-ergo-aero-road-bike-handlebar-actual-weights-01-1068x313.jpg 1068w\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/coefficient-RR-ergo-aero-road-bike-handlebar-actual-weights-01.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/coefficient-RR-ergo-aero-road-bike-handlebar-actual-weights-01-297x87.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/coefficient-RR-ergo-aero-road-bike-handlebar-actual-weights-01-800x235.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/coefficient-RR-ergo-aero-road-bike-handlebar-actual-weights-01-120x35.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/coefficient-RR-ergo-aero-road-bike-handlebar-actual-weights-01-768x225.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/coefficient-RR-ergo-aero-road-bike-handlebar-actual-weights-01-696x204.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/coefficient-RR-ergo-aero-road-bike-handlebar-actual-weights-01-1068x313.jpg 1068w\"></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-252273\">For comparison, a standard 44cm ENVE road handlebar is 218g. The 42cm Wave RR came in at 327g with guides.</figcaption></figure><p>The width of the aero tops vary by size, measuring 43mm, 45mm, 47mm and 49mm as bar widths go up. Weights range from 310g up to 325g.</p><p>Above, my 42cm bar weighed in at 327g <em>with</em> the cable sleeves still in it (bars shipped with these pre-installed to assist with internal routing)…so, it’ll drop a gram or two with those removed.</p><h2>Coefficient Wave RR first impressions</h2><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/coefficient-RR-ergo-aero-road-bike-handlebar-hand-positions-02.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/coefficient-RR-ergo-aero-road-bike-handlebar-hand-positions-02.jpg\" alt=\"different hand positions on the coefficient wave rr aerodynamic road bike handlebar\" width=\"1400\" height=\"1055\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1400px) 100vw, 1400px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/coefficient-RR-ergo-aero-road-bike-handlebar-hand-positions-02.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/coefficient-RR-ergo-aero-road-bike-handlebar-hand-positions-02.jpg 1400w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/coefficient-RR-ergo-aero-road-bike-handlebar-hand-positions-02-297x224.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/coefficient-RR-ergo-aero-road-bike-handlebar-hand-positions-02-800x603.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/coefficient-RR-ergo-aero-road-bike-handlebar-hand-positions-02-120x90.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/coefficient-RR-ergo-aero-road-bike-handlebar-hand-positions-02-768x579.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/coefficient-RR-ergo-aero-road-bike-handlebar-hand-positions-02-696x524.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/coefficient-RR-ergo-aero-road-bike-handlebar-hand-positions-02-1068x805.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/coefficient-RR-ergo-aero-road-bike-handlebar-hand-positions-02-557x420.jpg 557w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/coefficient-RR-ergo-aero-road-bike-handlebar-hand-positions-02-80x60.jpg 80w\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/coefficient-RR-ergo-aero-road-bike-handlebar-hand-positions-02.jpg 1400w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/coefficient-RR-ergo-aero-road-bike-handlebar-hand-positions-02-297x224.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/coefficient-RR-ergo-aero-road-bike-handlebar-hand-positions-02-800x603.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/coefficient-RR-ergo-aero-road-bike-handlebar-hand-positions-02-120x90.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/coefficient-RR-ergo-aero-road-bike-handlebar-hand-positions-02-768x579.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/coefficient-RR-ergo-aero-road-bike-handlebar-hand-positions-02-696x524.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/coefficient-RR-ergo-aero-road-bike-handlebar-hand-positions-02-1068x805.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/coefficient-RR-ergo-aero-road-bike-handlebar-hand-positions-02-557x420.jpg 557w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/coefficient-RR-ergo-aero-road-bike-handlebar-hand-positions-02-80x60.jpg 80w\"></a></p><p>You’ll notice that I did not run my brake lines inside the bar, and that’s because early inventory of the Wave RR was limited to 42cm wide bars. They come in 38, 40, 42 and 44 cm widths, and I’d typically want the 44. But I also wanted to test it prior to launch, so I’m “borrowing” a 42 until the 44 comes in.</p><p>As such, and because I didn’t have the spare barbs and small parts to re-do my hydraulic brake install, I kept the brake hoses external. But, honestly, I’d have to take an honest look at how the Wave RR would redirect those hoses anyway.</p><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/coefficient-RR-ergo-aero-road-bike-handlebar-on-bike-01.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/coefficient-RR-ergo-aero-road-bike-handlebar-on-bike-01.jpg\" alt=\"coefficient wave rr bars shown installed on road bike\" width=\"1200\" height=\"900\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/coefficient-RR-ergo-aero-road-bike-handlebar-on-bike-01.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/coefficient-RR-ergo-aero-road-bike-hand